It is used to change just a few characters of a variable.

data _null_ ;
phone='(312) 555-1212' ;
substr(phone, 2, 3)='773' ;
put phone=;
run ;

Result : The variable PHONE has been changed from(312) 555-1212 to (773) 555-1212.

